- If Pi references reappear, check whether they are repo-managed dotfile symlinks or runtime data under `~/.pi/agent/`. This commit removed repo-managed settings/extensions/install wiring and cleaned the live symlinks, but intentionally left runtime data alone.
- `install.sh` may still show unrelated dirty Codex skill symlink changes in the working tree after this commit. Those were present before this Pi cleanup and were intentionally left unstaged.
